output.sentences: My friend and I participated in a political march encouraging others to Vote Richard Tisei.
There was a moment dedicated to the women of the service.
There was also a show of support for the troops in the field as part of the event.
I got to listen to the drums from my place in the crowd, beating to the rhythm of the people's hearts.
Even the end of the procession was cool, we got to check out the interesting decorations on the car.
